{"tid":1403492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以點醒我","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:08:26.000Z","uid":203456,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37c59c3f7dd67a4b78d9ca0336c9772c523eb82b","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:34.000Z","msg":"有無人可以解釋下 每次遊行集會完 繼續留到咁夜嘅目的係咩 <br />\n成日都比藍絲問依個問題 自己又真係唔係好清楚 因為平時都係去遊行 行完未到夜晚就跟班fd走 <br />\n<br />\n自己夜晚睇直播好似成班人都等緊比人清場 等緊食催淚煙咁 咁多位手足比人捉咗覺得好嬲好可惜<br />\n呢排成日都想試下做多啲 試吓留夜啲幫手 所以希望咁多位可以解釋比我聽 等我有多啲動力去幫手 同時都可以解釋番比屋企人聽我地背後嘅原因係咩<br />\n<br />\n重申 不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰 <br />\n8月5日我會罷工<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"ba9f946f5e78332d328eb70a7532b91ab59328de","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:49.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"203735ab05313cd88fa744d95a3b1e21481531e6","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:59.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"64dfb95ff09fdad60f0c095963b7559a6bf68300","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"f88d17241aaf9f9bd5768ba778230459743ea4b4","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:20:22.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"9f31675e252301084d5d6fb7bbf8b1f71d1eaaf5","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:20:36.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"709a916e76373bfe937f6d326293ad854710fa9c","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:16.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"179cd5359a82db787115de4eedc9e638e2244b24","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"8月5日我會罷工"},{"pid":"514350f7b354978ea01d3efc1798c819d2911bec","tid":1403492,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":